oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Billy Block's Western Beat (Aug. 1)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Gallway, Peter; Lavery, Dan; McNally, Larry John; Payne, Harold; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue on gray) announcing Billy Block's Western Beat American Music Showcase featuring Lisa O'Kane, Wendie Colter, Peter Gallway, Dan Lavery, Mare Lennon, Larry John McNally, Harold Payne, James Coberly Smith, and John Townsend hosted by Matthew Lee at Highland Grounds in Hollywood, California on August 1. Poster features a metal photoplate of the Western Beat logo.
